quran[22]{c,v,t}:
  54,1,Ka toe that watee teuka kiamat Buleun di langet taeu ka beukah
  54,2,Teuma di jih dum ‘oh jieu ayat Jipaleng ligat sira jipeugah Nyan keubit sihe teuka lom laju
  54,3,Jikkheun paleusu kon nibak Allah Peuturot napsu di jih dum meuhat Teuma ka teutap putosan Allah Bandum ka teutap putosan Tuhan
  54,4,Ubak awaknyan ka lheuh geupeugah Haba peutakot soe nyang buet dacha
  54,5,Hikeumat raya peunteng that leupah Teuma peuingat hana meuguna
  54,6,Bah meunan teuma di jih lam salah Uroe nyan teuka ureueng jak meuhoi Bandum geumeuhoi jak keunoe bagah Haro-hara that jinoe ka teuka
  54,7,Khuchu‘ dum mata teumakot leupah Teubiet lam uruek dum lagee daruet Ka meuruet atuet le han ban peugah
  54,8,Bak ureueng jihoi jiplueng meuree-ree Kaphe dum teuntee leupah that susah Jikheun le kaphe uroe nyan meuhat Tanyoe meukarat hanaban peugah
  54,9,Kawom Noh dilee nibak awak nyan Jikheun sulet nyan peue nyang Noh peugah Hamba Kamoe nyan jikheun ka gila Bek le that haba jiyue top babah
  54,10,Teuma geulakee ubak Po gopnyan Neubri beu meunang lon nyoe ka kalah
  54,11,Kamoe peuhah treuk dum pinto langet Te raya that-that laju meuruah
  54,12,Bandum mata ie nyang na di bumoe Teupanca jinoe meulimpah-limpah le nyang di langet ngon nyang di bumoe Meusapat jinoe le han ban peugah Jeut treuk keu tophan teuma raya that Kheundak Hadharat han ek soe teugah
  54,13,U dalam kapai meupeuek gopnyan Papeun ngon labang ka meurok sudah
  54,14,Teuma meujaga ngon mata Kamoe Jijak kapai nyoe teuma le bagah Meunan keuh balah meubri keu gopnyan Nyang geuba iman deungon ikheulah Teuma jikaphe peue nyang gopnyan ba
  54,15,Jeut treuk keu tanda nyan Kamoe keubah Teuma na soe cok nyan keu peuingat
  54,16,Pakriban azeub keu jih Lon balah Nyan keuh dum ka troh nyang geupeuingat
  54,17,Qur'an pih that Kamoe peumudah Jeut nyan keu dike ingat keu Tuhan Teuma na soe nyan jitueng phaedah
  54,18,Meunoe pih sulet jipeugah le ‘Ad Pakriban azeub keu jih Lon balah Nyan keuh dum ka troh nyang geupeuingat
  54,19,Angen guncang that meukirem bagah Bak uroe ħahas keu jih ceulaka Buet angen raya guncang that leupah
  54,20,Jibot jibapo dum manusia Meutimpa-timpa mate dum reubah Sang bak kureuma reubah dum teubot
  54,21,Pakriban azeub keu jih Lon balah Nyoe keuh dum ka troh nyang geupeuingat
  54,22,Qur'an pih that Kamoe peumudah Jeut nyan keu dike ingat keu Tuhan Teuma na soe nyan jitueng phaedah